A Little Song of Life<br/><br/>GLAD that I live am I; 
<br />That the sky is blue; 
<br />Glad for the country lanes, 
<br />And the fall of dew. 
<br /><br />After the sun the rain; 
<br />After the rain the sun; 
<br />This is the way of life, 
<br />Till the work be done. 
<br /><br />All that we need to do, 
<br />Be we low or high, 
<br />Is to see that we grow 
<br />Nearer the sky. 
